UM\"\"\",出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-1,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,2,Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,13,\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"\"LS4PSXUNUM\"\"\",出现次数:2\\n', 'matched_anomaly': 'Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T10:10:24Z to 2025-06-20T10:30:24Z.', 'time_range': '2025-06-20 10:10:24+00:00 to 2025-06-20 10:30:24+00:00'}\n\n--- Node Pod Mapping ---\n{'aiops-k8s-01': ['emailservice-1', 'frontend-1', 'productcatalogservice-2', 'recommendationservice-2', 'shippingservice-0'], 'aiops-k8s-02': [], 'aiops-k8s-03': ['shippingservice-2', 'recommendationservice-1', 'adservice-0'], 'aiops-k8s-04': ['paymentservice-2', 'currencyservice-0', 'frontend-0', 'checkoutservice-0'], 'aiops-k8s-05': ['paymentservice-1', 'cartservice-1', 'checkoutservice-2'], 'aiops-k8s-06': ['productcatalogservice-1', 'emailservice-2', 'frontend-1'], 'aiops-k8s-07': ['shippingservice-1', 'emailservice-0', 'currencyservice-1', 'cartservice-0', 'adservice-1'], 'aiops-k8s-08': ['currencyservice-2', 'recommendationservice-0', 'paymentservice-0', 'frontend-2', 'checkoutservice-1', 'productcatalogservice-0', 'cartservice-2', 'adservice-2', 'redis-cart-0']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n根据收集到的日志数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **错误模式**：日志中频繁出现 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`，表明多个服务在尝试访问 `productcatalogservice` 时遇到了区域不可用的错误。\n2. **涉及服务**：\n   - **frontend**：抱怨无法从 `productcatalogservice` 获取产品或推荐信息。\n   - **productcatalogservice**：自身也报告了 `failed to query product by id` 的错误，进一步确认了问题。\n\n### 根因分析\n- **公共嫌疑人**：`productcatalogservice` 是多个服务抱怨的目标，且其自身也报告了错误，表明该服务可能因区域不可用而无法正常工作。\n- **错误类型**：`Region is unavailable` 表明可能是数据库或存储层的区域性问题。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"failed to query product by id\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable (Error 9005)导致无法查询产品信息\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的指标数据，我发现了多个异常信号。现在进行详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"duration_99th\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"store_unhealth_count\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库查询性能严重下降，duration_99th从0.01ms飙升到64.88ms，failed_query_ops出现异常峰值\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tidb的duration_99th变化率199.94%，p99值从0.01ms上升到64.88ms，同时failed_query_ops在p99分位出现55.22的异常值\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间rrt异常飙升，特别是productcatalogservice-1和productcatalogservice-2实例\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1的rrt从7576.59上升到19899629.86（变化率199.85%），productcatalogservice-2从6955.12上升到19975422.23（变化率199.86%）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个实例出现高错误率error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-1的error_ratio达到60.0%，shippingservice-0达到48.64%，shippingservice-2达到34.72%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务error_ratio和server_error_ratio异常升高，且pod_cpu_usage出现异常下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 error_ratio 20.0%，frontend-1 13.52%，frontend-2 14.56%；同时pod_cpu_usage从正常值下降到接近0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"存储健康状态异常，store_unhealth_count从0上升到0.5\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-pd的store_unhealth_count中位数从0上升到0.5，p99值从0上升到1.0，表明存储节点健康状态恶化\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n1. **核心问题**：TiDB数据库性能严重下降（duration_99th飙升199.94%）是系统故障的根源\n2. **连锁反应**：数据库性能问题导致依赖数据库的productcatalogservice响应时间异常飙升\n3. **服务级影响**：shippingservice和frontend服务出现高错误率，frontend服务CPU使用率异常下降可能表明服务降级或重启\n4. **存储层问题**：tidb-pd的存储健康状态异常，进一步证实了数据库层面的问题\n\n故障模式符合**数据库性能瓶颈导致依赖服务连锁故障**的典型场景。\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的链路追踪数据，我现在进行故障分析。从数据中可以看出明显的异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"productcatalogservice->TiDB\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'错误，这是TiDB数据库区域不可用的错误，表明底层数据库连接出现问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作从正常9-10秒延迟到39-40秒，延迟倍数达到4000倍以上，严重超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"错误消息'Region is unavailable'直接指向TiDB数据库的区域不可用问题，这是整个故障的根因\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点：**\n\n1. **根因定位**：ProductCatalogService是故障的源头，因为它直接返回TiDB数据库错误\"Region is unavailable\"\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - TiDB数据库区域不可用 → ProductCatalogService超时和错误 → Frontend服务返回500错误\n   - 影响扩展到CheckoutService，导致订单处理失败\n\n3. **延迟分析**：\n   - ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作延迟从9-10秒增加到39-40秒\n   - 延迟倍数超过4000倍，表明严重超时\n\n4. **错误类型**：数据库连接问题导致的超时和错误，而非网络问题\n\n故障根因是TiDB数据库的区域不可用，导致依赖它的所有服务（特别是ProductCatalogService）出现连锁故障。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "TiDB数据库区域不可用是系统故障的根因，导致productcatalogservice无法正常查询产品信息，进而引发前端服务连锁故障"}
